<p>Notice that promotional content is only 10%. The businesses that post 100% promotional content are the ones with 3 likes per post. The businesses that mix in community, behind-the-scenes, and educational content build the engagement that makes promotional posts actually visible.</p>
<h3>Posting Frequency</h3>
<p>Data from <a href="https://recurpost.com/blog/facebook-statistics/">RecurPost</a> shows Pages posting 10 times per week achieve the highest engagement rate at 1.61%. That is roughly 1 to 2 posts per day.</p>
<p>For most local businesses, 4 to 5 posts per week is a realistic starting point. Consistency matters more than volume. Posting 5 times per week every week outperforms posting 14 times one week and nothing the next.</p>
